	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />- In <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?p=48780#48780" class="postlink">this topic</a>, the <em>explode.nsf</em> fails in my emu. Could someone help me? From my first testing, it's not related with sweep or envelope...
<br />
<br />- Here's a <a href="http://rocknes.kinox.org/explosion.zip" class="postlink">WAV record package (20kb)</a> for you to listen. There are 2 files: explosion.wav is my emu output, megaman3.wav is how it should be played.

		

		</td>
