	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I checked explode.nsf in my player, and indeed the file tries to read from $4003 and $4007. Changing the return value of these reads from $40 to $00 gives the same effect as the file you recorded.
<br />
<br />If you do return correct values then I'm not sure what's wrong. I'd verify the return values.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


